@* Compares soft in-place navigation vs full page navigation using HTMX headers. *@
<section class="panel">
    <h2>Redirect Headers</h2>
    <p>Demonstrates `HX-Location` soft navigation vs `HX-Redirect` full redirect responses.</p>
</section>

<section id="redirect-demo" class="panel">
    <h3>Redirect Patterns</h3>
    <div class="demo-note" role="note">
        <strong>How To Test:</strong> soft redirect preserves the shell and swaps `#hrx-main-layout`;
        hard redirect forces a full navigation.
    </div>
    <p class="demo-caption">
        Expected outcome: both end at Home, but navigation mechanics differ (`HX-Location` vs `HX-Redirect`).
    </p>

    <button type="button" hx-post="/fragments/navigation/soft">Soft redirect (HX-Location)</button>
    <button type="button" hx-post="/fragments/navigation/hard">Hard redirect (HX-Redirect)</button>
</section>
